[SN]TITLE[SN]
Humber Bridge footpath to close for City of Culture display

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
People hoping to watch a large fireworks display on New Year's Day will not be able to use the Humber Bridge as a viewing platform, organisers have said.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
The "In with a Bang" display, near Hull Marina, will mark the beginning of Hull's year as UK City of Culture.
Managers of the Humber Bridge said it does not have the resource to manage a large number of people.
The bridge's east footpath will be closed until 20:30 GMT on 1 January.
